<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sq">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <title>Bileta u Anulua</title>
    <style>
        .cancel-container { max-width: 600px; margin: 100px auto; padding: 40px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #181b22 0%, #12151b 100%); border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.45); border: 1px solid rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.25); text-align: center; }
        .cancel-container h1 { color: #ffc107; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 32px; }
        .cancel-container p { color: #e8e8e8; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; }
        .cancel-details { background: rgba(14, 17, 21, 0.5); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0; border-left: 3px solid #ffc107; }
        .cancel-details h3 { color: #ffc107; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .cancel-details p { text-align: left; margin: 8px 0; color: #d0d0d0; }
        .action-buttons { display: flex; gap: 15px; justify-content: center; margin-top: 30px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .btn-back { background-color: #e50914; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn-back:hover { background-color: #b2070f; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <a href="/" class="logo">Kinema AAB</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Kthehu te Filmat</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="cancel-container">
            <h1>✓ Bileta u Anulua me Sukses</h1>
            <p>Ulësja juaj u çlirua dhe është disponuese për të tjerë.</p>

            <div class="cancel-details">
                <h3>📋 Detajet e Anulimit</h3>
                <p><strong>Filmi:</strong> <%= filmi %></p>
                <p><strong>Salla:</strong> <%= salla %></p>
                <p><strong>Ulëse:</strong> <span style="color: #ffc107; font-weight: 600;"><%= ulesa %></span></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 14px;">Shuma e paguar do të kthehet në metodën e pagimit të përdorur brenda 5-7 ditesh pune.</p>
            </div>

            <a href="/" class="btn-back">← Kthehu në Ballinë</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
